('bookkeeper-moex-01242', 'bookkeeper', 'bookkeeper-moex-104-a2a4e0d3', 'sub-bookkeeper-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '依現行稅捐稽徵法第48條之1的規定，納稅義務人在未經檢舉、調查前，自動向稅捐稽徵機關補報並補繳 所漏稅款者，下列敘述何者正確？ 加計利息免罰  加計利息減半處罰  免加計利息免罰  免加計利息減半處罰', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:29:26+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "e11ffe57731a", "answer_pdf_sha1": "8475d4e2817c", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "104170", "c": "602", "s": "1204", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "稅務相關法規概要", "year": "104", "exam_name": "104年專技建築師、技師、第二次食品技師、不動產經紀人、記帳士考試", "original_question_number": 3, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["incomplete_options"], "slug": "bookkeeper", "db_exam_id": "bookkeeper"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('bookkeeper-moex-01243', 'bookkeeper', 'bookkeeper-moex-104-a2a4e0d3', 'sub-bookkeeper-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '張無忌104年度之房屋稅繳款書，經臺北市稅捐稽徵處中正分處於104年4月20日送達。該房屋稅核定應 納稅額為10萬元，繳納期間為104年5月1日至5月31日（星期日），若張無忌於104年6月3日繳納 該稅款，依現行稅捐稽徵法規定，應加徵滯納金若干？ 0元  1千元  2千元  1萬5千元', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:29:26+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "e11ffe57731a", "answer_pdf_sha1": "8475d4e2817c", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "104170", "c": "602", "s": "1204", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "稅務相關法規概要", "year": "104", "exam_name": "104年專技建築師、技師、第二次食品技師、不動產經紀人、記帳士考試", "original_question_number": 4, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["incomplete_options"], "slug": "bookkeeper", "db_exam_id": "bookkeeper"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('bookkeeper-moex-01244', 'bookkeeper', 'bookkeeper-moex-104-a2a4e0d3', 'sub-bookkeeper-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '依現行稅捐稽徵法之規定，下列敘述何者錯誤？ 申請獲准延期或分期繳納稅款之期間不超過3年 納稅義務人因自行計算錯誤而溢繳之稅款，得於5年內申請退還 稅捐機關對復查之申請案，應於2個月內做成復查決定書 受理稅捐案件訴願之機關，應於6個月內做成訴願決定書', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:29:26+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "e11ffe57731a", "answer_pdf_sha1": "8475d4e2817c", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "104170", "c": "602", "s": "1204", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "稅務相關法規概要", "year": "104", "exam_name": "104年專技建築師、技師、第二次食品技師、不動產經紀人、記帳士考試", "original_question_number": 5, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["incomplete_options"], "slug": "bookkeeper", "db_exam_id": "bookkeeper"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('bookkeeper-moex-01245', 'bookkeeper', 'bookkeeper-moex-104-a2a4e0d3', 'sub-bookkeeper-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '根據現行稅捐稽徵法的規定，依法應由納稅義務人申報繳納之稅捐，已在規定期限內申報者，其核課期間之 起算日為： 申報日  申報期間屆滿日  申報期間屆滿之翌日  所屬徵期屆滿之翌日', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:29:26+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "e11ffe57731a", "answer_pdf_sha1": "8475d4e2817c", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "104170", "c": "602", "s": "1204", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "稅務相關法規概要", "year": "104", "exam_name": "104年專技建築師、技師、第二次食品技師、不動產經紀人、記帳士考試", "original_question_number": 6, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["incomplete_options"], "slug": "bookkeeper", "db_exam_id": "bookkeeper"}'::jsonb, NULL),
